Metadata: Sea Grant Fisheries (Spring, Summer, and Fall 2003)
University of California Sea Grant Extension Program
Restarting this new newsletter that was previously published for 27 years as the California Sea Grant Extension Program Newsletter

This newsletter will focus on marine fisheries, as part of the National Sea Grant fisheries extension initiative. Our goal is providing readers with fisheries information in a concise, non-advocacy, educational format. Main topics in these issues: Robert Price retires; Marine Life Management Act: Sea Grant's role; Collaborative research on juvenile rockfish habitat preferences; Trawl fleet buy-back referendum passes; California dungeness crab fishery survey.
